<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Interview With The Vampire</span>, <span>The Vampire Lestat</span>, <span>The Vampire Armand</span>, <span>Queen Of The Damned</span>, <span>Prince Lestat</span>, <span>Merrick</span>, <span>Memnoch The Devil</span>, <span>Blood And Gold</span>, <span>Blackwood Farm</span>, <span>Blood Canticle</span>, <span>The Tale Of The Body Thief</span> </h3>
